"Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-18_"><p class="sc-bJBfJu eVDjFe pf-19_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bOQUxc quwHz pf-21_">Image by monkeybusiness via Envato Elements</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a193" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-fsvrPk eTuePL pf-22_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-eNSrbD jPuwGZ"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-23_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-24_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-25_">Skills for life: Empowering future generations</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-27_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-93be98dc-1cad-46c8-997e-adeeead5290a"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">National Apprenticeship Week (NAW) 2025 is set to take place from 10th to 16th February, bringing together employers, apprentices, and training providers to celebrate the impact of apprenticeships on individuals, businesses, and the economy. This year’s theme, “Skills for Life,” highlights the vital role apprenticeships play in equipping individuals with lifelong skills that enhance career prospects and contribute to workforce development across various sectors.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-30_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-31_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-32_">Why do apprenticeships matter?</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-34_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-c8d97ead-eeea-4529-8abc-cd24e295d262"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Apprenticeships offer a unique blend of on-the-job training and academic learning, providing apprentices with hands-on experience while earning a wage. For businesses, apprenticeships serve as an opportunity to nurture talent, bridge skills gaps, and develop a highly skilled workforce.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-37_">Key benefits of apprenticeships
</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-39_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-40_"><strong>For apprentices</strong> - Gain practical experience, earn while you learn, and develop industry-specific skills.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-42_"><strong>For employers </strong>- Attract fresh talent, upskill existing staff, and boost business productivity.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-44_"><strong>For the economy</strong> - Drive innovation, enhance workforce capabilities, and support national employment goals.
</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-46_">National Apprenticeship Week 2025 - What to expect?</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-48_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a9044717-d594-4413-a603-4c447f475925"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">During the week, organisations across the UK will host events, webinars, and workshops to showcase the benefits of apprenticeships. Employers, training providers, and policymakers will share success stories, promote apprenticeship opportunities, and encourage individuals to consider this rewarding career pathway.
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-51_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-52_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-53_">Apprenticeships and career development</h3><p class="sc-dPZUdm eeluBw pf-55_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-b362442b-0286-4182-9c46-30dfc3a10688"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Apprenticeships not only provide essential workplace skills but also serve as a pathway to long-term career success. Many apprentices transition into full-time employment with their organisations, while others leverage their experience to pursue further education or even start their businesses.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-58_">Long-term benefits for apprentices
</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-60_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-61_"><strong>Enhanced career progression</strong> - Gain industry-recognised qualifications that improve job prospects.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-63_"><strong>Financial stability</strong> - Earn while you learn and reduce student debt compared to traditional education routes.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-65_"><strong>Networking opportunities</strong> - Build connections with industry professionals and mentors who can support career growth.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-67_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eoVZcn cepmFm pf-68_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ePDMnc jGJiiy pf-69_">How to get involved</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dhFVuh gFqzWs pf-71_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fbKhWw bnrVBh pf-72_"><strong>Employers </strong>- Showcase apprenticeship success stories within your business and explore funding opportunities to support new apprentices.
